    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is an excellent option for someone looking for reliable transportation at a more accessible price point. The exterior shows its history with some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and typical paint fading consistent with its age and mileage. Inside, the cabin is functional but displays visible wear on the upholstery and some of the high-touch surfaces. Mechanically, the car remains dependable for daily commuting, though it does not have the pristine feel of a newer model. It has been maintained to ensure it stays roadworthy and safe for its next owner.",
