    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled distinction. This specimen remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a history of meticulous preservation and fastidious care. Every aspect of this automobile, from its flawless exterior finish to its immaculate interior appointments, adheres to the highest standards of automotive excellence. For the discerning collector or enthusiast, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly peerless form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
